snippet.title: Range is HOT! Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn to shoot! Speed through courses with guns blazing. Learn target placements, increase your accuracy, and get the lowest time. Climb to the top of the leaderboards to be the king (or queen) of the range.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1503590/Range_is_HOT/
